title: Wallace D. Wattles-The Science of Being Great
description:
The Science of Being Great - The Practical Guide to a Life of Power

Wallace D. Wattles is hailed for introducing the world to the power of positive thinking and has had untold impact on countless lives with The Science of Getting Rich. Here Wattles delivers the ultimate companion piece to his groundbreaking work--and a book that is sure to inspire new levels of achievement for those who embrace its philosophies.

Greatness is within anyone's reach, as long as one knows how to tap into its source. In clear, concise fashion, Wattles reveals that there is a universal intelligence that any one of us can use to increase personal power and become more successful. Multitudes of Wattles' followers will attest that limitations of heredity and circumstance can be overcome by harnessing the creative power of the soul inherent in us all.
